Cash ISAs offer a safe place to save with tax-free interest, while Stocks and Shares ISAs allow you to invest in a wider range of assets, potentially offering higher returns but also carrying more risk. Lifetime ISAs are designed for first-time homebuyers or retirement savings, offering government bonuses.
